hopobject.body: I'd like to send this letter by zyalix llc Rae Ann Fera is a contributor for Co.Create whose specialty is covering the media, marketing, creative advertising, digital technology and design fields. She is also curator of Packaged Goods, a regular screening at TIFF Bell Lightbox featuring excellence in ads, videos, and shorts, and was formerly the editor of leading international ad industry publication Boards magazine.
